{"tid":530402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 約 老 公 睇 戲","createTime":"2018-01-15T17:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T19:35:14.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"befe7be3c9c38d0bbf4c18e7a6e61d3f0f511e5d","tid":530402,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"電影《西遊記女兒國》鐵定下月15日在香港上映，但為了搶情人節票房，內地與香港於下月14日會做點映，GiGi已經約定了老公情人節拍拖搶先睇優先場，GiGi指滿意自己的演出，唯一受不了特技化妝，雖然不是第一次，但肯定是最辛苦的一次，她表示：「每次拍戲前化妝要用5、6粒鐘，卸妝又要一粒鐘，如果開早班，凌晨4點就要起身化妝，好彩試片反應都話我表現唔錯，起碼辛苦都覺係值得。」GiGi又指給女兒Sofia看其演的國師造型照片，女兒完全認不出是媽咪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180115/large/15ec2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180115%2Flarge%2F15ec2p2.jpg&h=9eaefbd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6c194236d83396e109dac6c1a68acbe59306f17","tid":530402,"uid":166796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed2371b3184ab41a9acf48024ec6de0893b44c0f","tid":530402,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n西班牙籍老公呢</span>"},{"pid":"c418225566a46ae1ff03425e68ec04860339b091","tid":530402,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T19:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1d827419bc0b6dbd0c16d46a22d863036c3fbd","tid":530402,"uid":154907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T19:35:14.000Z","msg":"Sergio"}]}